# Typography System

## Font Families

### Open Sans (Body Text)
- Weights: 300, 400, 600, 700
- Use for: Body text, UI elements, navigation
- Tailwind: `font-sans` (default)

### Lora (Headings)
- Weights: 400, 500, 600, 700
- Use for: H1-H6, selected emphasis
- Tailwind: `font-serif`

## Heading Scale

```html
<!-- H1 - Page titles -->
<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif text-forest-green">
  Velkommen til AKD
</h1>

<!-- H2 - Section headers -->
<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-serif text-forest-green">
  Om os
</h2>

<!-- H3 - Subsection headers -->
<h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-forest-green">
  Vores historie
</h3>

<!-- H4 - Card titles -->
<h4 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif text-forest-green">
  Job & karriere
</h4>
```

## Body Text Scale

```html
<!-- Large body text (intros, leads) -->
<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-charcoal leading-relaxed">
  AKD er et moderne andelsselskab...
</p>

<!-- Regular body text -->
<p class="text-base md:text-lg text-charcoal leading-relaxed">
  Vi producerer kartoffelstivelse...
</p>

<!-- Small text (captions, metadata) -->
<p class="text-sm md:text-base text-charcoal/70">
  Publiceret 12. november 2024
</p>
```

## Links

```html
<!-- Inline link -->
<a href="#" class="link-mint">
  Læs mere
</a>

<!-- Link with arrow -->
<a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-mint hover:text-forest-green transition-colors">
  Se alle stillinger
  <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
</a>
```

## Emphasis

```html
<!-- Bold for key facts -->
<p class="text-charcoal">
  AKD producerer <strong class="font-semibold text-forest-green">175.000 tons</strong> kartoffelstivelse årligt.
</p>

<!-- Italic for quotes -->
<blockquote class="italic text-lg text-charcoal border-l-4 border-mint pl-6">
  "Vi investerer i fremtidens bæredygtige løsninger"
</blockquote>
```
